-- #816 adversarial break 4: the callback carries <Stdout> on effect var <e>
-- but the return row is bare <e> — an impl applying the callback pours the
-- atom into a row a caller instantiates to <>.  Rejected at the interface
-- declaration by T-EFFECT-ARG-UNCOVERED (post-unify inspection cannot see it:
-- the same-tail row arm loses the atom).
interface Act a where
  act1 : a -> (Unit -> <Stdout | e> Unit) -> <e> Unit
